Selected `_prompts` (underscore prefix) as the git notes ref for prompt storage (`refs/notes/_prompts`) to make it distinct from memory namespace categories (decisions, patterns, learnings, etc.). This avoids confusion with the `prompts` namespace and prevents ref conflicts with `refs/notes/subcog`.